@TestClass(value="org.openscience.cdk.smsd.interfaces.AlgorithmTest")
public enum Algorithm
extends java.lang.Enum<Algorithm>
implements java.lang.Comparable<Algorithm>

This class represents various algorithm type supported by SMSD. Presently SMSD supports 5 different kinds of algorithms:

  1. 0: default,
  2. 1: MCSPlus,
  3. 2: VFLibMCS,
  4. 3: CDKMCS,
  5. 4: SubStructure
  6. 5: TurboSubStructure

Author:
Syed Asad Rahman
